channel.title: No-ip
channel.description:
first off. i portforwarded with utorrent. i used a tutorial from this http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,383567.0.html and then i downloaded no-ip and i made a host. then i refreshed and updated my window thing on the no-ip DUC window that shows my hosts. and then i opened my server up, and tried to log on from my host i made on no-ip. it said error connecting to server. but then i go to use my hamachi ip and i can get on fine. what am i doing wrong???? and how do i make it so other people can get on? when i first started out with my server, i went on random hamachi networks and told people to join. i got like 5 people to download my client and play. but when they go to log in it says error connecting to server. i just want to host a 317 private server without hamachi and with no-ip. :confused: please help me
i tried to put it on the RUNE Locu$ server status page( http://www.RUNElocus.com/status/ it put google instead of RUN3 L0CU$ so replace the google with the real url) and then i click submit and it says its offline. but i know for a fact its online because i open the source window and it says its online. i dont get it.?!
